{"id": 57814, "date": "2025-07-26T04:00:10", "date_gmt": "2025-07-26T11:00:10", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=57814"}, "modified": "2026-03-12T12:03:23", "modified_gmt": "2026-03-12T19:03:23", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-july-26-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/26/kingdom-of-days-july-26-2/", "title": {"rendered": "July 26"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1974:\u00a0</strong>A planned gig opening for Dr. John in San Diego is cancelled due to low ticket sales.</p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their second of back-to-back nights at Kutztown State College, where Bruce debuts his cover of &#8220;Carol.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/rZt6J4vYmHw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/fmrbPsTI8Pw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1981:\u00a0</strong>Bruce is sick, causing his scheduled River Tour show in Cincinnati to be postponed.</p>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>Bruce&#8217;s third and final night in Toronto on the Born in the U.S.A. Tour is a great one, featuring the live debut of &#8220;My Father&#8217;s House,&#8221; the tour premiere of &#8220;Who&#8217;ll Stop the Rain,&#8221; and a rare (on this tour, at least) &#8220;Ramrod.&#8221; The entire second half of the show plus encores is professionally filmed.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/gHMliZEuQk0?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/2qExWoSEyg8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/txqSkn996J8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/w6C5U3pHtqg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/W64OapCpnN4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/56qib3oWvhA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/z3WKifIG5yM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div id=\"v-J5MtQW5J-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/J5MtQW5J?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1992:\u00a0</strong>At the third of eleven Meadowlands shows on World Tour 1992, Bruce closes the evening with the tour premiere of &#8220;Jersey Girl,&#8221; the first performance of that song in almost seven years.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/08AOp1JK6cQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div id=\"v-q1Gx2eoy-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/q1Gx2eoy?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1999:\u00a0</strong>The opening stand of the U.S. leg of the Reunion Tour reaches Night Five (of fifteen) at the Continental Airlines Arena in East Rutherford.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/pjnIjTCfg-s?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div id=\"v-axOeGGb5-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/axOeGGb5?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/UmEDu3P5AtY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2002:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play an afternoon Rising Tour rehearsal show at Asbury Park&#8217;s Convention Hall before an audience of contest winners. Bruce plays &#8220;Countin&#8217; on a Miracle&#8221; for the first time, and &#8220;Into the Fire&#8221; features Clarence on bagpipes (that arrangement will not make it to the tour itself). &#8220;Glory Days&#8221; also makes its return, which surprisingly was not played at all during the Reunion Tour. That evening, Bruce surprises the concert winners when he shows up at Sonny&#8217;s Southern Cuisine and takes requests.</p>\n<div id=\"v-9mLG5EG4-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/9mLG5EG4?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28478\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2002-07-26-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2002-07-26.png?fit=1139%2C1747&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1139,1747\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2002-07-26\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2002-07-26.png?fit=196%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2002-07-26.png?fit=668%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28478 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2002-07-26.png?resize=758%2C1163&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1163\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2002-07-26.png?w=1139&amp;ssl=1 1139w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2002-07-26.png?resize=196%2C300&amp;ssl=1 196w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2002-07-26.png?resize=668%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 668w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2002-07-26.png?resize=768%2C1178&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2002-07-26.png?resize=1001%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1001w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2003:\u00a0</strong>Night Six of ten at Giants Stadium on the Rising Tour opens with the tour premiere of &#8220;Adam Raised a Cain.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-VOlqU4JY-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/VOlqU4JY?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>2005:\u00a0</strong>At his solo acoustic show at the Greensboro Coliseum, Bruce tour debuts &#8220;Two Hearts&#8221; and plays &#8220;If I Should Fall Behind&#8221; on the pump organ for the first time.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ttl4D69Tvx8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xtxymKvlhsQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"57819\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/26/kingdom-of-days-july-26-2/news_and_record_2005_07_28_18/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/News_and_Record_2005_07_28_18.jpg?fit=2339%2C2071&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2339,2071\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"News_and_Record_2005_07_28_18\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/News_and_Record_2005_07_28_18.jpg?fit=300%2C266&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/News_and_Record_2005_07_28_18.jpg?fit=758%2C671&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-57819 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/News_and_Record_2005_07_28_18.jpg?resize=758%2C671&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"671\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/News_and_Record_2005_07_28_18.jpg?w=2339&amp;ssl=1 2339w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/News_and_Record_2005_07_28_18.jpg?resize=300%2C266&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/News_and_Record_2005_07_28_18.jpg?resize=1024%2C907&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/News_and_Record_2005_07_28_18.jpg?resize=768%2C680&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/News_and_Record_2005_07_28_18.jpg?resize=1536%2C1360&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/News_and_Record_2005_07_28_18.jpg?resize=2048%2C1813&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/News_and_Record_2005_07_28_18.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"57820\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/26/kingdom-of-days-july-26-2/news_and_record_2005_07_28_46/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/News_and_Record_2005_07_28_46.jpg?fit=1501%2C1173&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1501,1173\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"News_and_Record_2005_07_28_46\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/News_and_Record_2005_07_28_46.jpg?fit=300%2C234&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/News_and_Record_2005_07_28_46.jpg?fit=758%2C592&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-57820 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/News_and_Record_2005_07_28_46.jpg?resize=758%2C592&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"592\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/News_and_Record_2005_07_28_46.jpg?w=1501&amp;ssl=1 1501w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/News_and_Record_2005_07_28_46.jpg?resize=300%2C234&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/News_and_Record_2005_07_28_46.jpg?resize=1024%2C800&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/News_and_Record_2005_07_28_46.jpg?resize=768%2C600&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2009:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band take the Working on a Dream Tour into its European home stretch, winding up the leg with a five-show mini-tour of Spain, starting with this first show in Bilbao. &#8220;Does This Bus Stop at 82nd Street&#8221; and &#8220;You Never Can Tell&#8221; both get the tour premiere treatment.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/6pJmgGAePro?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/3wmW2AVO2AI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Um5dq7Dbi2s?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#